headline: Chewy Stock Sees Relative Strength Rating Run Higher
summary: Chewy stock had its Relative Strength (RS) Rating upgraded from 64 to 72 Thursday — a welcome improvement, but still shy of the 80 or higher score you look for.  This unique rating identifies technical performance by showing how a stock's price action over the last 52 weeks compares to that of the other stocks in our database.

headline: Iconic Tonics Launches Award-Winning Klaus THC-Infused Libations and NEIN by Klaus, a Premium RTD Line with Botanical Terpene Infusion
summary: Snoop Dogg's Iconic Tonics today announced the launch of Klaus, a collection of ready-to-drink, THC-infused libations crafted by critically acclaimed mixologist and author Warren Bobrow. Klaus is available in regulated cannabis markets in New York, made with premium live rosin, and hemp-derived Delta-9 THC varieties sold at select retail locations and via DoorDash in New Jersey, as well as nationwide DTC.
